      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_fan-02.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、今日は私達のライブを観に来てくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ thank you so much for coming",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_fan-03.m4a",
      "text": "本当にありがとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to see our live performance today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5066665173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.2666666508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんとライブ……本当に……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A live… with sister…? really…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2666666508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.8690925758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-10.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、琴乃からもみんなにご挨拶しないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ Kotono‚ you should greet everyone too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8690925758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.4357598146
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "え……ええと、いつか一緒にステージに立てたらって\n昔、二人で話をしたことがあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… well‚ a long time ago‚ we talked about\nhow nice it would be if we could stand on stage together someday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.5983901183
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "その時は、そんなことある訳ないって思いましたけど\nでも……今日、やっとその夢が叶いました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ I thought something like that could never happen‚\nbut… today‚ that dream finally came true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.7666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.7568259716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-08.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃もねぇ、昔は私よりちっちゃくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know‚ Kotono used to be smaller than me‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7568259716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いつも私の後ろをくっついて来たんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "always trailing right behind me wherever I went.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1204256378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.9568253358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-04.m4a",
      "text": "いつの間にやら、私より背が伸びちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before I knew it‚ you grew taller than me‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9568253358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "琴乃の頭も撫でられなくなって、寂しいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and now I can’t even pat your head anymore. It makes me a little lonely~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.7950218488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.6568294049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "もう……お姉ちゃんってば、昔からいくら言っても\n私の髪をくしゃくしゃにするの、やめてくれないよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey… no matter how many times I tell you‚\nyou never stop messing up my hair‚ sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.5671020668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-14.m4a",
      "text": "だって、ちょうどいいところに頭があるんだも～ん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s because your head is at the perfect height~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.5671020668,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2199.5645999000003,
          "startTime": 59.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.3004354001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "私も、もう高校生になったんだけど\nお姉ちゃんには、まだ頼りないままなのかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m already a high school student now‚\ndo I still seem unreliable to you…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.4333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.9241544565
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_no-02.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないよ。今はステージでも頼れる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not true at all. I believe",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.9241544565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "立派なアイドルだと思ってますとも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "you’re a fine‚ dependable idol on stage now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.0971456468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.1574885528
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-12.m4a",
      "text": "私が言うのもなんなんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if it sounds strange coming from me‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1574885528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私の妹ってことで、琴乃は随分苦労したと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think you’ve had a hard time just because you’re my little sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7693062835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.1241531849
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いつも私と比べられて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "People always compared you to me‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1241531849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "姉は『星降る奇跡』だったのに、って言われて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "saying‚ “Your sister was a ‘Starry Miracle.’”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3574865341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.3908208688
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sister…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.3908208688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.1986419916
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-13.m4a",
      "text": "でも琴乃は、私なんかが心配するまでもなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Kotono didn’t need someone like me worrying about her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1986419916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こんなに大きく、立派になってくれました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She grew up so strong and wonderful on her own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.0310859065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.1319778681
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-01.m4a",
      "text": "胸を張れるようなことばかりじゃなかったけど……\n事務所のみんなにも、迷惑かけてばかりだったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wasn’t always something I could be proud of…\nI caused so much trouble for everyone at the agency‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.7319809199
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まぁ、いろいろやらかしてたよねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you did mess up in all kinds of ways.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.7319809199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.7653096756
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-08.m4a",
      "text": "お正月に、マネージャーにお年玉をもらおうとして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like trying to get New Year’s money from the manager",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.7653096756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でも素直に言わないせいで、大事になったりとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and making it a big deal because you wouldn’t ask honestly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.8879488595,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-04.m4a",
          "delay": 945.3814220999988,
          "startTime": 118.8333302816
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.1986409744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
